.g-body-title Import an existing tape archive (TAR) file from the filesystem
.g-body-subtitle= folder.name()

p.
  Pass an absolute path (or a path relative to the current assetstore) to a tape archive on
  the filesystem that is exposed to the Girder server. Note that you must be granted
  special permission to do this by the administrators of this server.

form.g-tar-import-form
  .form-group
    label(for="g-tar-import-path") Import path
    input#g-tar-import-path.form-control.input-sm(type="text", placeholder="E.g. my.tar.gz")
  .g-validation-failed-message
  button.g-submit-tar-import.btn.btn-success(type="submit")
    i.icon-link-ext
    |  Import TAR
